Wow, his hair messed up shortly after I ran.

554
00:36:45,220 --> 00:36:47,840
Why are you running after me?
Winwin's hair is messed up.

555
00:36:48,110 --> 00:36:49,810
Winwin, don't cry.

556
00:36:49,930 --> 00:36:51,360
Give it back, Kana.

557
00:36:51,480 --> 00:36:54,480
Winwin doesn't want to be with you.
Didn't you see his tears?

558
00:36:55,500 --> 00:36:56,510
It's mine.

559
00:36:58,040 --> 00:36:59,580
It's okay, Winwin.

560
00:36:59,800 --> 00:37:00,890
Sit down, Kana.

561
00:37:01,264 --> 00:37:03,334
It's okay.

562
00:37:12,670 --> 00:37:14,430
Please comb his hair, Pai.

563
00:37:14,440 --> 00:37:15,850
Barbie, what is it?

564
00:37:34,740 --> 00:37:35,950
What is it?

565
00:37:36,710 --> 00:37:37,870
I've paid for it all.

566
00:37:42,140 --> 00:37:44,630
Is it your hospital donation letter?

567
00:37:47,500 --> 00:37:50,390
I just got the same one at school.

568
00:37:55,770 --> 00:37:57,020
Why did they send it?

569
00:37:58,430 --> 00:38:02,480
Hey! This is Palmthip's wedding invitation,
Park's ex-girlfriend.

570
00:38:07,020 --> 00:38:08,680
But she probably didn't invite you.

571
00:38:10,120 --> 00:38:11,700
She definitely sent this to ridicule you.

572
00:38:12,820 --> 00:38:16,970
Yes, she just wanted to say
she found a better husband than you.

573
00:38:19,180 --> 00:38:19,990
Yes.

574
00:38:20,310 --> 00:38:23,920
She was very mean to send her
ex-boyfriend a wedding invitation.

575
00:38:24,840 --> 00:38:28,950
I remember well how she hurt my husband.

576
00:38:31,660 --> 00:38:33,120
You are the devil!

577
00:38:33,120 --> 00:38:36,220
Stop! It seems you guys are more angry than me.

578
00:38:38,090 --> 00:38:39,950
I'm not that regretful.

579
00:38:42,500 --> 00:38:47,160
No regrets? You broke your heart
and played a Bogie Dodge song.

580
00:38:47,620 --> 00:38:50,410
You've been crying loudly
through the house for months.

581
00:38:52,160 --> 00:38:53,480
It's a 'Got Dumped' song, right?

582
00:38:53,857 --> 00:38:54,717
Yes.

583
00:38:56,246 --> 00:38:59,726
~Do you know who got dumped?~

584
00:38:59,750 --> 00:39:01,740
Hey! Stop!

585
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:04,610
Crazy kids.

586
00:39:05,410 --> 00:39:09,970
Isn't it a crazy kid like me who is
always by your side when you're sad?

587
00:39:18,650 --> 00:39:20,380
Are you okay?

588
00:39:21,200 --> 00:39:22,430
I didn't feel anything.

589
00:39:24,197 --> 00:39:25,227
Forget it.

590
00:39:28,490 --> 00:39:30,650
Will you go to her wedding?

591
00:39:39,880 --> 00:39:41,180
I won't.

592
00:39:43,060 --> 00:39:46,390
It's the same day as your birthday.
I have to be with you.
